{"id":179226,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2011/09/美国之音-世贸原址今昔和未来/","date":"2011-09-15T00:30:34Z","modified":"2011-09-15T00:30:34Z","title":"美国之音 | 世贸原址今昔和未来","content":"<p><div><img height=\"52\" src=\"http://media.voanews.com/designimages/icon-voanewsLogo-print.jpg\" width=\"165\" /></div>\n<div>\n<div>\n<div>\n<div>\n<h1><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://mrss.dokoda.jp/r/http://www.voanews.com/chinese\"><img border=\"0\" height=\"72\" src=\"http://media.voanews.com/designimages/blank.gif\" width=\"220\" /></a></h1>\n</div>\n<div>\n<p><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://mrss.dokoda.jp/r/http://www1.voanews.com/chinese/about-us/contact/\">联络我们</a> | <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://mrss.dokoda.jp/r/http://www.voafanti.com\">繁體</a> | <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://mrss.dokoda.jp/r/http://www.voanews.com/chinese/\">简体</a></p>\n<p><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://mrss.dokoda.jp/r/http://www.voanews.com/chinese/news/Ground-Zero-Then-and-Now-129532753.html\"></a>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div>\n<ul>\n<li>2011年 9月 12日</li>\n<li>\n<div>\n<ul>\n<li><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://mrss.dokoda.jp/r/http://www.voanews.com/chinese/news/20110912-WORLD-ECONOMY-129673043.html\">希腊偿债能力遭质疑 全球市场重挫</a></li>\n<li><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://mrss.dokoda.jp/r/http://www.voanews.com/chinese/news/20110912-soviet-sports-china-129650273.html\">中国体育成就缘于苏联经验？</a></li>\n<li><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://mrss.dokoda.jp/r/http://www.voanews.com/chinese/news/20110912-china-suicide-prevention-129646783.html\">面对高自杀率 中国主办防自杀大会</a></li>\n<li><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://mrss.dokoda.jp/r/http://www.voanews.com/chinese/news/20110912-dpp-tsai-us-129639598.html\">蔡英文启程赴美，批马访大陆计划</a></li>\n<li><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://mrss.dokoda.jp/r/http://www.voanews.com/chinese/news/Ground-Zero-Then-and-Now-129532753.html\">世贸原址今昔和未来</a></li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n</li>\n</ul><option value=\"\">选择语言</option><option value=\"/oromoo/\">Afan Oromo</option><option value=\"http://www.voanews